This project was developed to build a docker-compose with multiple elasticsearch cluster, Logstash, Metricbeat, filebeat and Kibana. 
The Goal is to configure the lifecycle to parse the data over the elasticsearch cluster (HOT, WARM AND COLD)


DEPLOY 
To deploy the stak is just type: docker-compose up -d  
and acess in the browser  youripadress:5601

How configure the lifecycle 

https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/master/set-up-lifecycle-policy.html#:~:text=To%20create%20lifecycle%20policies%20through,policy%20to%20the%20Elasticsearch%20cluster.



Machine Resources. 
STORAGE : 2 TB SSD 
MEMORY: 64 GB RAM DD4 2400 
CPU: XEON SILVER 12 CORE 24 virtualization
OS: CENTOS 7




